_sText:
Hello. This is my first released ZombieMod map in here.
This map has only few camping spots, and it's not very big map.
But i'll be working on this map more later.(On v2's, v3's, etc.


Map has: Cellar, 2 Ways to come back to surface/Go down to the cellar.
1 Way to get in the house, has 2 Flats. From the house you can go to the market.

Map presents:

Secret door - Close the door by pressing a button in 1 of the regular camping spots. Open again by going down the small house and breaking the invisible wall, then press the button.

And alot more! =)


Pictures:
A= Terrorist spawn
B= A camp place
C= CT Spawn
D= The small market.
E= Trapdoor

Edits:
Added new version, Zm_I_T_A_L_Y__1 = Cage has been remade a bit.
Added new version again,=Zm_I_T_A_L_Y_2= added a market, and made map look a bit better.
Zm_I_T_A_L_Y_3= Edited market a bit, more camping spots, longer cellar, terrorists and counterterrorists spawn at other places.

Goals:
